  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbrääms nahze Saru\nnoschehloht / un wiꞥnu aprau-\naht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pehz zehlahs Ahbrääms /\no fawa Mirrohu / un runnaja\nr Etta Behrneem/ fazzidams:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es eſmu weens Sweschi-\neeks/ pee jums/ misdams/ Doh-\net man ihpaſchu Kappu/tad es\nprakſchu fawu Mirrohu / no\nannahm Azzim nehſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad athildeja Etta Behr-\nAhbräänam/fazzidami us to:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Klausi muhs / Knugs / tu\ni weens Deerviſkas Wirfneeks\nulfo widdii/aprohzi tawn Mir-\nan muhfös zeenigös Kappös/\nweenam no mums/ buhs tew\nvu Kappu aisleegt/ ka tew ne\nhtu Waltas / tawu Mixrohu\nraſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlabs Ahbrääms /\nflannijahs preeſch teem Sem-\ns Laudim preeſch Etta Behr-\nm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥschrunnaja ar teem/\nidams: Ja tas junis irr pa\nabtam/ ka es fawn Mixrohu\nnna Preeſcha aprohku / tad\nafajt mann / un aisluhdseet\nnnis deht Eewronu Zōira\nhlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka tas man dohd tawu diw-\ntiqu Bedri / kas tam fawa\nruma Gallá irr / tam buhs\nn to par pillu Nandu doht/\nweenu ihpaſchu Kappu juhfo\ndu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Eewrons mitte starp\nEtta Behrneem : Tad athil-\ndeja Eewrons tas Eetiteris Ah-\nbräänam/ preeſch Etta Behrnu\nAufim/un preeſch wisfeem/ kas\nzaur winna Pilsfahta Wahrtim\ngahje/ fazzidams.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne/ mans Knugs/ klaufi\nmann / to Tihrumu dohnu es\ntew/ un to Bedri / kas eekſch ta\nirr / to dohnu es tew / preeſch\nmanuo Lauschu Behrnu Azzim\ndohnu es tew to / aprohz tarut\nMirrohu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad flannijahs Ahbra-\nains preeſch teem Semmes Lau-\ndim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un runnaja us Eewronu/\nteem Semnes Laudim dsirdoht/\nfazzidains: Mihtajs/ ja tu grib-\nbi/ klaufi mann luhsanis: Es\ndohchu tew to Nandu preeſch\nta Tihruma / nemm to no man-\nnim/ tad aprakſchu es tur fawu\nMirrohu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Eewrons athildejaAh-\nbräänam/ fazzidams us to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Maus Knugs/ klaufi\nmann / ta Semme makfa tschetr-\nsints Sudraba Sihketus / zik\ntas irr starp man/ un starp tew/\naprohz tikfai tawu Mixrohu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbrääms paklaufija\nEewronam/ un eefwehre tam to\nNandu/ ka tas bij runnajs teem\nEtta Behrneem dsirdoht/ tschetr-\nsints Sudraba Sihketus/ kas\nPrezzinecku Starpa tekk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ktüa winnan Eew-\nrona Tihruns par ihpaſchu /\neeſch\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
